From d3836b137b66a69d299fc12cd17191ec33756db1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: edde746 <86283021+edde746@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Thu, 7 May 2026 19:05:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] videotoolbox: disable native DV session for profile 7

FFmpeg's HEVC hwaccel path only forwards parameter NALs and VCL slices to
VideoToolbox. Profile 7 conversion therefore does not feed converted RPUs
into the compressed samples sent to VT. Keep P5/P8 on the Apple DV path,
but decode P7 as plain HEVC HDR base layer.
---
 libavcodec/videotoolbox.c | 3 ---
 1 file changed, 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/libavcodec/videotoolbox.c b/libavcodec/videotoolbox.c
--- a/libavcodec/videotoolbox.c
+++ b/libavcodec/videotoolbox.c
@@ -852,9 +852,6 @@ static int videotoolbox_dovi_is_apple_hevc(const AVDOVIDecoderConfigurationRecor
     if (!dovi || !dovi->rpu_present_flag || !dovi->bl_present_flag)
         return 0;
 
-    if (dovi->dv_profile == 7)
-        return 1;
-
     switch (dovi->dv_profile) {
     case 5:
         return 1;
